OL,3,GCentral, Tayside & Fife
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FRain is
OL,6,Fexpected to spread northeast through
OL,7,Fthe evening and overnight, this may be
OL,8,Fheavy for a time. Then becoming dry
OL,9,Fwith clear spells by morning.
OL,10,
OL,11,CSaturday:FIt will be dry and warm
OL,12,Fthrough the day with some prolonged
OL,13,Fbright or hazy sunny spells.
OL,14,
OL,15,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FWarm
OL,16,Ffrom Sunday to Tuesday with plenty of
OL,17,Fbright or sunny spells in the east,
OL,18,Fcloudier at times in the west on
OL,19,FSunday. Perhaps a bit cloudier on
OL,20,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
